<tool name="set_appended_messages_path">
  <description>Set the dataset message-list path appended to runs for the currently mounted playground.</description>
  <use_when>
    - The user asks to append, set, change, or clear the conversational message history used for message-based dataset re-runs.
    - The user wants playground runs to include a list of messages drawn from a dataset row.
  </use_when>
  <rules>
    - The `path` points at a dataset message-list to append for conversational/message-based re-runs.
    - Pass an empty string or null for `path` to disable appending.
    - This tool only updates browser UI state. It does not edit prompt messages or run the playground.
    - This setting applies to the loaded dataset. If no dataset is loaded, call `load_dataset` first.
  </rules>
</tool>
